What you need to know:

Karauri spoke to Nation Sport in Nairobi on Friday, at the sidelines of an event where SportPesa Foundation donated Sh1.2 million worth of equipment to the new maternity wing at Riruta health facility in Nairobi CountyHarambee Stars have been pooled alongside Uganda, Rwanda and Mali in the qualification matches for the 2022 Fifa World CupKarauri also says the betting firm is keen on supporting athletes who have struggled to make ends meet owing to the disruptive nature of the sports calendar